      <title>特斯拉利用周末降低汽车和 FSD 软件价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/tesla-cuts-china-us-prices-after-sales-slow-inventories-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于销量下滑和库存过剩，特斯拉公司上周末下调了其在中国、欧洲和美国的车型价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/tesla-cuts-china-us-prices-after-sales-slow-inventories-rise</guid>
