    <item>
      <title>中国新股领军企业面临越来越多的贸易调查浪潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/trade-tensions-threaten-the-rise-of-china-s-stock-champions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国最有前途的行业正面临西方政府日益增长的贸易限制威胁，这使得有潜力推动中国市场增长的股票前景变得模糊。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/trade-tensions-threaten-the-rise-of-china-s-stock-champions</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TikTok 剥离或禁止法案预计将在几天内成为美国法律</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/tiktok-divest-or-ban-bill-expected-to-become-us-law-within-days</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国众议院周六提出一项立法，迫使 TikTok 的中国母公司字节跳动有限公司剥离其所有权股份，该法案很快就会成为法律，并将其与对乌克兰和以色列的一项重要援助计划挂钩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/tiktok-divest-or-ban-bill-expected-to-become-us-law-within-days</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 17:15:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>七大财报伴随股市关键时刻到来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/magnificent-seven-earnings-arrive-with-stocks-at-critical-moment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大型科技公司的财报将于下周公布，对于那些寻求人工智能推动暴跌的标准普尔 500 指数反弹的投资者来说，恰逢其时，该指数刚刚经历了一年多来最糟糕的一周。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/magnificent-seven-earnings-arrive-with-stocks-at-critical-moment</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 11:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰要求苹果、谷歌合作打击军事赌博</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/war-in-ukraine-zelenskiy-enlists-apple-google-in-military-gambling-crackdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基已禁止该国军队内赌博，因为担心赌博会削弱士气并在对抗俄罗斯入侵的过程中构成安全风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/war-in-ukraine-zelenskiy-enlists-apple-google-in-military-gambling-crackdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 10:20:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克以特斯拉义务为由推迟印度之行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/elon-musk-postpones-india-visit-to-later-in-the-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克(Elon Musk)推迟了对印度的访问，其中包括与总理纳伦德拉·莫迪(Narendra Modi)会面，称他必须解决特斯拉公司的紧迫问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/elon-musk-postpones-india-visit-to-later-in-the-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 04:53:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OpenAI 猛烈抨击马斯克的“修正主义历史”，试图撤销诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/openai-slams-musk-s-revisionist-history-in-bid-to-toss-lawsuit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OpenAI 表示，埃隆·马斯克声称该公司为了追求利润而放弃了利他原则，这只不过是“修正主义历史”，也是为了提振其竞争对手的人工智能公司的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/openai-slams-musk-s-revisionist-history-in-bid-to-toss-lawsuit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 03:46:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币“减半”减少了对矿工构成威胁的新代币供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/bitcoin-halving-cuts-supply-of-new-tokens-in-threat-to-miners</link>
      <description><![CDATA[备受期待的比特币软件更新“减半”已经完成，这对那些通过确保数字货币平稳安全运行来赚钱的公司来说是一个潜在的打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/bitcoin-halving-cuts-supply-of-new-tokens-in-threat-to-miners</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 00:10:52 GMT</pubDate>
